The reporter assessed the event apathy, executive dysfunction and  neurological decompensation as medically 
significant.
The reporter assesed aphasia as permanently disabling because of partial language aphasia.
No further information was provided.
Additional information received on 24/Sep/2015. Following information was added to case: Reporter was added. 
